  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK990">
<l>cāṉṟavar cāṉṟāṇmai kuṉṟi ṉirunilantāṉ</l>
<l>ṟāṅkātu maṉṉō poṟai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If there is a defect in the character of the perfect, (even) the great world cannot bear (its) burden.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
